{"tid":616216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高鐵出軌】港鐵員工短訊流傳出事前維修中心閘門「無故震動 」","createTime":"2018-04-04T04:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T04:18:35.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"14a5afab06d0b2acbc3512c4391f843257c70e47","tid":616216,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"正進行試行的廣深港高速鐵路（香港段），周二晚（3日）發生罕見列車出軌意外，事件迅速在港鐵員工的Whatsapp群組內流傳，港鐵則在凌晨2時向傳媒發稿證實事件。<br />\n<br />\n根據員工群組流傳的版本，涉事列車（編號EMU0256）昨夜7時許返回石崗列車停放處，並以慢速進入有蓋維修中心，職員在閉路電視發現中心閘門無故出現震動，列車司機一度停車並下車查看，不過未有發現，於是繼續開車慢駛，列車隨即出軌。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵其後在凌晨2時發稿公佈涉事出軌意外，指昨晚約9時15分，車廠工程人員進行巡查時發現一列停泊於維修車庫的高鐵列車，其尾卡部份車輪偏離路軌，事件中無人受傷；該列列車在昨日較早時進行試運行後，返回石崗列車停放。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，非常關注有關情況，將就事件進行詳細調查，並已通知機電工程署。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180404/58032048?_ga=2.243609920.4576743.1522808112-1389631860.1511919358\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180404%2F58032048%3F_ga%3D2.243609920.4576743.1522808112-1389631860.1511919358&d=1uZDcsoodVH09zhp3MIPiPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=af0ddd78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180404%2F58032048%3F_ga%3D2.243609920.4576743.1522808112-1389631860.1511919358&h=e09b54bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180404/58032048?_ga=2.243609920.4576743.1522808112-1389631860.1511919358</a>"},{"pid":"7e0b64f62b0ac76feae03ef500439c342ab43d58","tid":616216,"uid":1781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03fe80b7846b39814aa1aa57001b42593528a28","tid":616216,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:18:35.000Z","msg":"Sorry我車震搞到咁"}]}